
<span class='GTTabs_titles'><b>Translation</b></span><br />
Dududu dududu&#8230; dududu dududu dudu&#8230;<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, if we sang the whole night long<br />
To laugh and to scare our cares away, it&#8217;s party today<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, we go for a walk on the music scale<br />
Our heart filled with notes in flames to warm up our souls</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll sing, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
We&#8217;ll dance, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
Everyone unveils himself, tonight it&#8217;s the ball<br />
It&#8217;s the carnival, the carnival</p>
<p>Dududu dududu&#8230; dududu dududu dudu&#8230;<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, outside in the twinkling night<br />
All the lamps are shining in the eyes of the girls<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, we have the right to be a little crazy<br />
Laugh nose to nose, cheek to cheek, mock everything</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll sing, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
We&#8217;ll dance, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
Do what pleases us, tonight it&#8217;s the ball<br />
It&#8217;s the carnival, the carnival</p>
<p>Dududu dududu&#8230; dududu dududu dudu&#8230;<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, tonight money is forbidden<br />
We throw coins and notes like confetti<br />
Hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies, the fear for tomorrow is gone<br />
And we&#8217;ll be feeling good for a long time, hand in hand</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll sing, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
We&#8217;ll dance, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
Finally we&#8217;re living our life, tonight it&#8217;s the ball<br />
It&#8217;s the carnival, the carnival</p>
<p>We&#8217;ll sing, hey, hey, gentlemen, ladies<br />
